  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Analytics Companies We allow analytics companies to use tracking technologies to collect information about our users computers or mobile devices and their online activities These companies analyze this information to help us understand how our sites and apps are being used Certain versions of our App have an Opt out of Tracking setting which permits you to opt out of being tracked by third party analytics companies</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

